     Ericol "Longshot" Larethian is the son of a grey elf noble sudduced
by a drow elf female. His father is a member of the high council of the
Valley of the Mage in Greyhawk. Longshot was raised by his father's people
thus being an assassin in his early years. Now 175 years old(21 in human
years) he has given up the assassin lifestyle and is fulfilling his destiny
as champion eternal of the abermud realms.
     Longshot appears to be a normal grey elf with silver hair, cold steel grey
skin, violet eyes, and standing about 5 and a half feet tall. he wears 
black leather ranger garb with a crimson cloak. 

